        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Ban Corporate PACs Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits for-profit corporations from establishing or operating a separate segregated political fund (commonly known as a political action committee or PAC). Existing funds must terminate not later than one year after the date of enactment of this bill.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
